Bootstrap
---------
1. Bootstrap is a Html, css and javascript framework, used to create a responsive web page.

2. We can also use media query to make our page responsive but the best choice to make web page responsive is BOOTSTRAP.

3. Bootstrap works on classes. There are several classes available to make html elements responsive like we have button class to make button attractive , container class to make container responsive, image class to make images responsive and many more.

4. Internally bootstrap also uses media query to make web page responsive.

5. Bootstrap is an open source and cross platform, which means we can download bootstrap from internet free of cost.

6. Bootstrap is compatible with almost all modern web browsers.

7. Bootstrap provides consistent design.
8. There are several versions of Bootstrap is present in the market, out of which we go through with Bootstrap3,4 and 5.